hadiths[10]{hadithnumber,text}:
2492,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jiska khajuron ka baagh ho ya zamin ho to wo usey na bechey jab tak apney shareek ko pesh kaash! na kerey."
2493,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jiskey paas zamin ho aur wo usey bechna chahey to usey chahiye ke apney hamsaaey ko) kharidney ki) pesh kaash! kerey."
2494,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hamsaaya apney hamsaaey key Shufey ka ziyada haq rakhta hai. agar (hamsaaya) ghair hazir ho to us (key Shufey) ka intizar kya jaey jabke un dono ka raasta eik ho."
2495,"Hazrat abu-Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hamsaaya apney qarib ki jagah (makaan ya zameen) ka ziyada haq daar hai."
2496,"Hazrat shareed bin Suwed Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool! wo zamin jis mein kisi ka hissa ya sharaakat nahin, sirf ham-saayegi hai (uska kya hukm hai?) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hamsaaya apney qarib ki jagah ka ziyada haq daar hai."
2497,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ghair taqseem shuda chiz (zameen ya makaan) mein Shufey ka faisla farmaya. jab had bandi ho jaey to phir koi shufa nahin . Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney apney doosrey ustad Muhammad bin Hammad Tahrani key wastey sey bhi ye riwayat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey isi tarah bayan ki hai. (hadees key Raavi) abu-Aasim (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : Saeed bin Musaiyab ki Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat mursal hai. aur abu-Salma ki Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat muttasil hai.
2498,"Hazrat abu-Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : shareek apney qarib ki (mushtarak) jagah ka ziyada haq daar hai jo kuch bhi ho."
2499,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney har us chiz mein shufa muqarrar kya hai jo taqseem na ki gaee ho. jab had-bandi ho jaey aur raastey alag-alag ho jaeyn to phir koi shufa nahin ."
2500,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : shufaa oont ki rassi kholney ki tarah hai. (jis tarah rassi khulney sey oont fauran azad ho jata hai, isi tarah shufey ka dawaa fori tor par qabile-qubul hai. junhi zamin ya makaan ki farokht ki khabar miley to dawa kerey. baad mein ye dawa qabile-qubul nahin hai.)"
2501,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik shareek ko doosrey shareek par shufey ka haq nahin, jab wo is sey pehley kharid ley. na chhotey (naabaaligh) bachey ko haq shufaa hasil hai, na ghair hazir ko ."
